VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (APP_KEY|SECRET|API[_-]?KEY|TOKEN|PASSWORD)\s*[:=]\s*[\'\"][^\'\"]{8,}[\'\"]
WHEN EXPR MISSING:example|sample|dummy|test|placeholder
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects likely hardcoded secret material in source/config.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Drupal Hardcoded Secret Material.
